{"tid":2045703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"七名英國前外相罕有聯合為香港發聲：為香港事務成立國際小組　英國在法律道德上對港人有責","createTime":"2020-06-01T03:22:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T08:25:45.000Z","uid":339805,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"799386e7aaf0dd92e45a8a29f6ef6a8134be43a7","tid":2045703,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T03:22:47.000Z","msg":"七名分別來自保守黨和工黨的英國前外相罕有聯合為香港發聲，要求英國政府就香港事務成立國際聯絡小組。<br />\n<br />\n英國《衛報》指，這次跨黨派行動反映英國政界的憂慮 &mdash; 國際間對中國事務的回應，不能單靠美國總統特朗普，英國有責任主動領導國際社會，呼籲成立類似 1994 年設立的巴爾幹聯絡小組，跟進香港事務。該小組讓國際社會團結一致討論波斯尼亞和科索沃問題。<br />\n<br />\n全文睇：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%83%E5%90%8D%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8%E7%BD%95%E6%9C%89%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%2583%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%25BD%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%2F&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGgogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=1915486b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%2583%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%25BD%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%2F&h=020ab245\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%83%E5%90%8D%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8%E7%BD%95%E6%9C%89%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2/</a>"},{"pid":"ca12c94997410065717de1f2bf80d69df0106e20","tid":2045703,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T03:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkg